                                 Warnings and Precautions (5.2)

                              ].

GOMEKLI tablets for oral suspension: can be swallowed whole or can be dispersed in drinking water and administered orally as a liquid [see 

   Dosage and Administration (2.4)

].

For patients who are not able to swallow whole tablets, prepare GOMEKLI tablets for oral suspension dispersed in drinking water and administer orally as a liquid [see 

                                 Instructions for Use

                              ].

